### REMEMBER TO CALL GET TOKEN FROM token.http

### First page, default size
GET https://localhost:7068/api/videos/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Explicit page/pageSize
GET https://localhost:7068/api/videos/my?page=1&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Second page
GET https://localhost:7068/api/videos/my?page=2&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Out-of-range page -> empty items, correct totalCount
GET https://localhost:7068/api/videos/my?page=999&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
